================================================================================
Network Specifications
================================================================================

INTcoin Network:
- Total Supply: 221 Trillion INT
- Block Time: 2 minutes (120 seconds)
- Mainnet P2P Port: 2210
- Mainnet RPC Port: 2211
- Lightning Network: Ports 2213-2214
- Address Format: Bech32 with 'int1' prefix

Post-Quantum Cryptography:
- Digital Signatures: NIST Dilithium Level 3 (FIPS 204)
- Key Encapsulation: NIST Kyber-768 (FIPS 203)
- Hash Function: SHA3-256 (FIPS 202)

